title: 823 41 "The Emperor Rolls Over! Rescue Brook Mission!"Transliteration: "Yonko no Negaeri – Burukku Kyūshutsu Dai Sakusen!" (Japanese:四皇の寝返り　ブルック救出大作戦！) Hiroyuki Satō Atsuhiro Tomioka January 28, 2018(2018-01-28)
